      • SetupProcess

        public SetupProcess()
             throws javax.sound.midi.MidiUnavailableException,
                    java.lang.InterruptedException,
                    javax.sound.midi.InvalidMidiDataException
        Initiates the setup process. Searches for the launchpad and calls the methods that open input and output ports if one has been found.
        Throws:
        javax.sound.midi.MidiUnavailableException - Midi Unavailable Exception
        java.lang.InterruptedException - Thread Interrupted Exception
        javax.sound.midi.InvalidMidiDataException - Invalid Midi Data Exception

        Searches a midi device that's description contains the name given
        Parameters:
        name - Name or portion of the name to search for
        display - Boolean: true if console output of the positions should be displayed, false otherwise
        Returns:
        True if found input and output ports for the device, false otherwise
